32
00:01:40.644 --> 00:01:43.093
<i>e sinto essa vontade
porque eu sou homem</i>


33
00:01:47.359 --> 00:01:49.174
<i>eu posso, sim</i>

34
00:01:56.159 --> 00:01:57.585
